JOB BEST PRACTICES
1. cluster -  always use job cluster/serverless
2. databricks runtime - use the latest LTS runtime
3. cluster reuse - for all the tasks use same cluster
4. enable photon -  for high performance
5. repair and re-run - if job failes instead of running againg from the start use repair which runs from the failed tasks
6. late jobs - enable notification for long running jobs
7. run as service principle - to get all the right previlage

